latestPosts.caption:
Sabr and Shukrana 🙏🏻🤍🧿 for all the times you’ve been, for all the times you’ve healed
for all that I’m learning, for all that I’m receiving, for all the times that broke me but for all the times that made me. For all the strength and courage, for all the love and opportunities. In good times and in bad, in my highs and lows, In prayers and in joy! 🙏🏻 I’m so grateful for everything. I’m slowly coming to terms with my past and learning to live in the present and only looking forward to what’s yet to come. Such a blessing to be able to make it back here whenever my heart has longed for it. I found my peace, I found my calling. I found myself. 🤍

latestPosts.caption:
Maybe it’s my faith or maybe it’s your divine presence… but everything big or small starts to align when I do your dhyaan and remember Nanak sahib and my Mahadev.. 🔱 You remind me that life is meant to be lived with simplicity, faith, love, and laughter... 
You appear in my dreams, in signs, in moments of silence and chaos.. and even though you’re beyond this realm now, you never truly left. You continue to guide us, love us, bless us, I strongly feel it every passing day! And for that- I am unendingly grateful.. Shukrana Guruji , Har Pal.. 🙏🏻

Sada banaaye rakhna, Mehr banayi rakhna aur hum sabko hamesha apni sharan mein rakhna, te simran di daat dena🤍🕊️ 
Jai Guruji🤍🧿
